			<h1 class="storytitle"><a href="http://markos.gaivo.net/blog/?p=133" rel="bookmark">iPod talk this Wednesday</a></h1>

			<div class="post-text">
				<p>I&#8217;ll be giving a talk this Wednesday at 19:00 in <a href="http://www.kiberpipa.org/index.php?module=ContentExpress&amp;file=index&amp;func=display&amp;ceid=6&amp;meid=25">Kiberpipa</a> as <a href="http://markos.gaivo.net/blog/?p=113">promised</a> some time ago. The theme of the talk will be lessons learned from iPod about (web) design and everyone is welcome to attend.</p>
<p>I&#8217;m buying a drink for everyone, who&#8217;ll manage to stay through my rather short talk and won&#8217;t flee the scene immediately afterwards. The talk will probably be given in English.</p>
			</div>

